---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Navbar from "../components/Navbar.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy — Cold Email Checker"
  description="Privacy Policy for Cold Email Checker. Learn how we handle your data when you use our free email spam checker tool."
  keywords="privacy policy, cold email checker privacy, data protection"
>
  <Navbar />
  <main class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6 py-16">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-ink">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-mute">Last updated: June 8, 2026</p>

    <div class="mt-10 space-y-8 text-body leading-relaxed">
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-medium text-ink">1. Introduction</h2>
        <p class="mt-2">Welcome to Cold Email Checker (coldemailchecker.com). We respect your privacy and are committed to protecting any information you share while using our service.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-medium text-ink">2. Information We Collect</h2>
        <p class="mt-2">Our spam checker tool processes email content entirely in your browser. We do <strong>not</strong> store, transmit, or log the email content you enter into our tool.</p>
        <p class="mt-2">We may collect:</p>
        <ul class="mt-2 list-disc pl-6 space-y-1">
          <li>Anonymous usage analytics (page views, feature usage)</li>
          <li>Device and browser information for compatibility purposes</li>
          <li>Information you voluntarily provide via contact forms</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-medium text-ink">3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <p class="mt-2">Any collected information is used solely to improve our service, fix bugs, and understand how users interact with our tool. We do not sell or share your data with third parties.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-medium text-ink">4. Cookies</h2>
        <p class="mt-2">We use minimal cookies for theme preference storage and basic analytics. No tracking cookies from third-party advertisers are used.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-medium text-ink">5. Third-Party Services</h2>
        <p class="mt-2">We may use privacy-respecting analytics tools to understand usage patterns. These services do not track you across other websites.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-medium text-ink">6. Data Security</h2>
        <p class="mt-2">Since email content is processed client-side and never sent to our servers, your email data remains on your device at all times.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-medium text-ink">7. Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p class="mt-2">We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated revision date.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-medium text-ink">8. Contact Us</h2>
        <p class="mt-2">If you have questions about this Privacy Policy, <a href="/contact" class="text-ink underline">contact us here</a>.</p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>
